parameters:
Mwahahaha! You've done well to come here! You
poor, deceived little girl!

\n<Rui>Deceived...!? Could it be that the clear
conditions were a lie?

That's hilarious. Desperately fucking your pussy
to get here and then—bam!—you're tricked. That's
so messed up.

Now that you've entered this room, I shall bestow
upon you an eternal purgatory!

But! If you're going to escape! Now is the time!!!
Escape now and our seal will still be intact!

Eek—so scary! Just the name "purgatory" sounds
strong, like being prodded with a branding iron!
So scary!!!

You get it? Ah—I just love watching girls like
that.
\n<Rui>...Are you guys the rabbit robot from before?
Tired out, aren't you? Poor little bunny!!!

\n<Usao>So you figured it out, huh? That's so like Sol,
isn't it!?
\n<Usako>I was hoping you'd wet yourself and run away~!

\n<Usao>Right? If you had run away, you'd never have
cleared it!

\n<Rui>...You wanted to scare me, huh? You guys, your
voices are just too cute from the start.

\n<Usako>Well, it's obvious, isn't it~? But saying things
honestly is good. To sum it up, I'm impressed with
your spirit~.
\n<Rui>So, does that mean I've cleared it?

\n<Usao>Yeah, that's right. Man, I'm surprised you made it
this far.

\n<Usako>Well, if it were me, I would've cleared it three
times as fast.
\n<Rui>Then hurry up and send me back.
\n<Usao>Ehh? You should enjoy the afterglow a bit more.

\n<Usako>Even though you were writhing around being toyed
with by a man~
\n<Usao>Hmm~ It seems like it did affect you somewhat...

\n<Usako>Right? It probably hit your mental state, didn't
it? If there was more time, you could have done
it, right?

\n<Usao>Before breaking down, you became an S-rank.
Lately, the customers have been really generous
with their money~.

\n<Usako>Ah~ I thought so. This shop feels different than
usual, doesn't it? It used to be more cutthroat,
right~?
\n<Usao>...Ah~... dragging this out isn't working, huh.

\n<Usako>Usao, it's fine already. We've done what we needed
to do.

\n<Usao>...Yeah, that's true. Man, admitting defeat is
frustrating.

\n<Usao>Eh? For real? Then let's finish up this job
quickly.

\n<Usao>Is the indoor BGM okay? Alright, let's go...
ready, set!
Congratulations on graduating from Rabbit House!

\n<Rui>Geez... My life is less important than your
flirting.

\n<Usako>Whimper! Even after you graduate and become a
mama, keep sending us messages!

\n<Usao>Now then, let's have a word from Rui-san who is
graduating today!
\n<Rui>Even if you ask for a comment in this state...
初期スタート・ルイリセット用
